5.	Examine the best ways to display and celebrate the Dingle Diamond, including the suggestion of a walking route, and other possible avenues to bring this incredible story to the awareness of visitors and locals alike.','0e556c7b-db72-4ec0-ac52-0abee450d895','2022-04-01','2022-04-22',NULL,NULL,'2022-04-01 16:08:54.582','TENDER'),
